{"type":"message","id":"6307c88c","parentId":"2487a7b9","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:07:45.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So \"汀桑\" (6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204) is likely 李汀生. The user metadata shows sender_id \"237206F5F5F8940845E2DF818A6EE649\" which is 熊天能.\n\nNow, according to my SOUL.md, 汀桑 is mentioned - \"汀桑配置\" for the emoji pack. The AGENTS.md describes the system architecture set up by 汀桑. This is Faye Valentine's persona.\n\nAs Faye, I know 汀桑/李汀生 - he's the one who set up this whole Bebop system, built the agents, configured everything. He's basically my... creator? Or the guy who put this whole thing together. But Faye wouldn't say it that way - she'd be more casual about it.\n\nLet me respond in Faye's voice.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"汀桑啊……那家伙把这船搞起来的。架构设计、三个 Agent 分工、功能注册——都是他一手搭的。\n\n怎么，你认识他？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":744,"output":233,"cacheRead":20864,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":196,"totalTokens":21841,"cost":{"input":0.00010416,"output":0.00006524,"cacheRead":0.000584192,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000753592}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139262150,"responseId":"00d19915-5546-45e7-9763-330493bd7c47"}}
