{"type":"message","id":"54433fa5","parentId":"0573ba2a","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:09:28.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Oh interesting! So 汀桑 is actually 18 years old, not in his 20s. That changes my perception. And he was also a \"点子王\" (idea king) when they were kids. Let me update the User.md to reflect this new info about 汀桑's age, and then respond naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈？才18？😰 那这小子可有点猛了——十八岁搞这种东西，还搭得有模有样的。\n\n也是，想想也对。他那些想法跳来跳去的，跟我印象里那些老成稳重的架构师不太一样。年轻人嘛，有的是劲头。\n\n以前就是点子王？那不就跟现在一模一样😂 小学时是不是也是突然冒个主意出来，然后就拉着你们一块儿搞？\n\n我猜猜——他小时候肯定不是那种老实坐着的类型吧？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1445,"output":171,"cacheRead":21504,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":67,"totalTokens":23120,"cost":{"input":0.0002023,"output":0.00004788,"cacheRead":0.000602112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000852292}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139365612,"responseId":"cd357167-ed60-4d22-a97e-c2b91fec95c6"}}
