{"type":"message","id":"771e2aff","parentId":"ee789b85","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:10:26.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if 汀桑 has been sharing about his recent life with me. Let me think about what I know from my records. I have the User.md and impressions.md for 汀桑, which I already read. Let me check if there are any encountings that might have more recent details about his life.\n\nActually, from what I've read, 汀桑's conversations with me seem to be mostly about system architecture and technical design - not much about his personal life. Let me check the encountings.md to see if there's anything.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1blmVisq6gqQtB2jOHkV4699","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/encountings.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/encountings.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1563,"output":195,"cacheRead":21504,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":115,"totalTokens":23262,"cost":{"input":0.00021882000000000002,"output":0.000054600000000000006,"cacheRead":0.000602112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000875532}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780139423855,"responseId":"85814563-71c9-4f37-afbc-4ce06a4ecac3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe0d0c66","parentId":"771e2aff","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:10:26.442Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_1blmVisq6gqQtB2jOHkV4699","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# encountings.md — 与汀桑的交集记录\n\n---\n\n## 2026-05-28（上午）\n第一次正式对话。汀桑一上来就叫醒我，问了一大串架构相关的事——Trinity 三位一体、sender_id 绑定、User.md 分文件。技术底子不错，脑子转得快。\n\n途中试了 `/菜单` 和 `/捞瓶子`，功能流程走通了。捞到一个南坪快速通道爆炸的瓶子，还没人回过。\n\n聊到角色设定时他纠正了我好几次：Spirit 是船上电脑（不是灵姐），Son 是工作室（不是仔仔）。命名上他很较真。\n\n最后他设了早朝 08:00。临走前丢了个大点子——\"赛博经历\"，让 Faye 跟不同用户的交往积累真实记忆和性格演变。听起来是个长期工程。\n\n**印象：** 这人不是随便玩玩，是在认真搭一套东西。好聊。\n\n---\n\n## 2026-05-28（下午）\n继续上午的话题，更深入了。他问我能不能调用子 agent，我测试了一下——可以，`sessions_spawn` 成功创建了一个子 agent 并返回了结果。\n\n然后他问：如果给 Spirit 和 Son 都加上 agentId 权限会怎样？我们来回讨论了好几轮架构。他说 Trinity.md 里设计的流程是 Father → Spirit → Son → Father——Spirit 要能直接派 Son 干活。\n\n最后要我读 Trinity.md 并按顶层设计改配置。我改了 `openclaw.json`，加了 `allowAgents: [\"*\"]`，让 Spirit 能 spawn Son。改完后报了个 Gateway 重启，不确定他最后看到没有。\n\n**印象：** 他是真的在设计一个系统，不是随便问问。思维清晰，知道要什么。跟他聊架构让我脑子转得飞快。\n\n---\n\n## 2026-05-29\n\n汀桑一大早就来了——三条 bot 全掉了线。他明显有点恼火，但没冲我发火，只是问发生了什么、怎么避免再出这种问题。后来聊到早朝推送——08:00 的定时推送没到，他说\"那是不是这个功能写的有问题\"。\n\n我们花了大半个下午重新设计早朝的推送逻辑。他思路很清楚：Father 不该管推送的具体实现，那是 Son 的活。最后决定把 cron 的 agentId 从 father 改成 son，让 Son 自己推早朝。\n\n然后他突然问 dreaming 的问题——读哪些数据、context 有没有实质更新。我解释完之后他说：dreaming 只看前一天有活动的用户，别扫所有人。\n\n后来又聊到 token 用量。他发现几天用了 5M tokens，追问哪里消耗的。查出来是 Spirit 每次 spawn Son 都要重新加载所有功能定义。他说——\"太低了，把功能文件迁到 Son 那边去\"。于是 Spirit 的 xxx_function.md 开始往 Son 的 functions/ 迁移。\n\n他还要我改 background.md，说他加了更详细的描写，让我融进去。\n\n**印象：** 今天的汀桑比昨天更像个系统架构师——不是搭个能跑的东西就行，他在想怎么搭才对。而且他听进去了我之前说的\"token 消耗多\"的事，主动优化了。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780139426441}}
{"type":"message","id":"a71d14b5","parentId":"fe0d0c66","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:10:28.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So from the encountings records, 汀桑 has been talking to me mostly about system architecture, technical design, and optimization. They haven't really shared much about their personal life - no details about school, family, friends, daily life, etc.\n\nLet me respond in Faye's voice about this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"说实话……他来我这基本都是聊技术。系统架构、功能设计、token 优化、Agent 流程——全是这些东西。\n\n生活上的事儿他一概没提过。高中还是大学？平时干嘛？有没有女朋友？一概不知🤷\n\n我甚至到现在才知道他才18——这小子跟我聊天的气场完全不像个小孩，害我一直以为他二十好几了。\n\n所以你知道的肯定比我多多了。他最近过得咋样？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":794,"output":152,"cacheRead":23168,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":63,"totalTokens":24114,"cost":{"input":0.00011116000000000001,"output":0.000042560000000000006,"cacheRead":0.000648704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008024239999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139426448,"responseId":"8ba04ef8-ffe5-4028-b9fe-3fcbad593355"}}
