{"type":"message","id":"7360102f","parentId":"04d289f0","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:11:08.676Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (熊天能) is saying they haven't seen 汀桑 much since elementary school graduation, last met him for a movie during Chinese New Year last year. They're asking me what I know, and I've already told them he only talks tech.\n\nLet me respond naturally in Faye's voice.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那咱俩凑一起也拼不出他现在的生活全貌啊😂\n\n他来我这全聊技术，你这边小学毕业就没怎么见了——中间这几年他干嘛了，没人知道。\n\n不过照我跟他聊这几天的感觉……这小子八成把自己关在房间里捣鼓 AI 系统呢。十八岁能搞出这个，平时估计没少熬夜🙈\n\n下次他来找我，要不我帮你问问他在干嘛？就说他老同学熊天能关心一下😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1480,"output":163,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":64,"totalTokens":24299,"cost":{"input":0.00020720000000000002,"output":0.000045640000000000003,"cacheRead":0.000634368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000887208}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139465430,"responseId":"9bba3f4a-d4f4-45dc-a349-b55eb4f80976"}}
