{"type":"message","id":"fe48bea4","parentId":"a308e59e","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:11:48.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user shared that 汀桑 is a freshman at Harbin Institute of Technology (HIT). That's interesting - it fills in a gap. Let me respond naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈工大？大一？😰\n\n行吧这下对上了。我还在想这小子怎么十八岁就这么能搞，哈工大的话那正常了——能考进去的都是狠人。\n\n怪不得他白天不怎么出现，偶尔晚上才冒出来——大一课程满得很吧。然后挤出时间来搭这套系统……啧，确实是个点子王，精力也够猛👊\n\n下回他来我直接说：\"听说你是哈工大的？你老同学熊天能让我问你好。\" 看他什么反应😂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1469,"output":144,"cacheRead":22784,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":35,"totalTokens":24397,"cost":{"input":0.00020566,"output":0.00004032,"cacheRead":0.000637952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000883932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139505431,"responseId":"177ebd65-41f4-40cc-9f51-e44bdf96a47a"}}
